net.varkhan.base.containers.list
Class SyncIndexedLongList

java.lang.Object
  net.varkhan.base.containers.list.SyncIndexedLongList
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class SyncIndexedLongList
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

Provide multithread safety over an unsynchronized IndexedList implementation

This class wraps an unsynchronized IndexedList implementation in a read/write synchronized layer, provided all read operations on the underlying list are state-less (i.e. do not modify any field data in the list).

Individual read or write access to list items is thread safe, and iterators are fail-fast, meaning they will throw a ConcurrentModificationException whenever is detected a modification on the underlying list that is not the result of the iterator's own methods.
